<item>
            <title>[NET-494] FTPClient.CSL.cleanUp() fails to restore timeout value on exception</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NET-494</link>
                <project id="12310487" key="NET">Commons Net</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The CSL class temporarily resets the socket timeout.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The cleanUp() method restores the original setting, however this may be skipped if an exception occurs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The code should ensure that the original setting is always restored.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
