                            <comment id="13674214" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Tue, 4 Jun 2013 10:10:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I took a look at why the current code needs Java 1.6, and concluded that it was not essential to use Java 1.6.&lt;br/&gt;
